@using Blazor.DesignSystem.Components

<PageTitle>Warning text - GOV.UK Design System</PageTitle>

<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Warning text</h1>
<p class="govuk-body">Use the warning text component when you need to warn users about something important, such as legal consequences of an action.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">When to use this component</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">Use warning text to highlight important information. Only use it when the consequences are serious, for example a fine or imprisonment.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Examples</h2>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Default warning text</h3>
